# Wikipedia App Using Docker Compose

This python utility consumes wiki api & read articles based on articles.txt file & stores the data in mongodb.
FastAPI app is created to run word count on this data stored in mongodb.

# Technical Stack

1. Python
1. Mongodb
1. MongoExpress
1. FastAPI
1. Uvicorn

## How to Run

Use docker compose to created the containers.

http://localhost:8081/	## MongoExpress
http://localhost:8000/wordcount/{word} ## FastAPI app